observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor, through the Municipality’s
HRMO, shall:
a.) fill up the vacant positions in the LGU plantilla in accordance with
CSC rules and regulations, subject to Personnel Services limitation;
b.) pay the mandated daily minimum wage prescribed by the RTWPB for
Region VIII;
c.) reduce the number of Job Order Workers so that the functions of the
existing regular employees are not duplicated by the JOs;
d.) submit the corresponding copies of Contract of Service of all Job
Order personnel as proof of wages paid to avoid audit suspension.
